/p>
<p>This week, Pastor Ray teaches on the reality of spiritual warfare and shares five strategies that Satan uses to defeat God's people:</p>
<ol class="boxed">
<li>Doubt</li>
<li>Disgrace</li>
<li>Disunity</li>
<li>Deceit</li>
<li>Dread</li>
</ol></div>